# {{ (boilerplate_name | default(project_name)) | title }}: {{ boilerplate_description | default(description) }}

## What is This Template?

This is a **Copier template** that scaffolds {{ boilerplate_type | default('CLI') }} projects with production-ready structure and all expected deliverables. When you need to create a new {{ boilerplate_type | default('CLI') }}, use this template to generate a complete, well-structured starting point.

### Quick Start

To generate a new {{ (boilerplate_type | default('CLI')) | lower }} project:

```bash
copier copy {{ template_path | default('./boilerplate/path') }} ./path/to/new-{{ (boilerplate_name | default(project_name)) | lower | replace(' ', '-') | replace('_', '-') }}
```

Answer the prompts to customize the template with your project details, and you'll have a complete project ready to go.

### Ticket Tracking

This project uses the **tkr** tool (<https://github.com/levonk/tkr>) for ticket tracking and task management. When working with template improvements:

- **Track your work**: Create tickets for template enhancements using `tkr`
- **Follow the workflow**: Use `tkr ready` to get the next actionable ticket, `tkr start` to begin work
- **Document changes**: Update tickets with notes about template improvements or issues found
- **Maintain quality**: Ensure all template work is tracked and reviewed through the ticket system

