## Usage Patterns

### Basic Usage

```bash
# Generate project with defaults
copier copy {{ template_path }} ./my-project --defaults

# Generate with custom inputs
copier copy {{ template_path }} ./my-project \
  --project-name=my-awesome-project \
  --include-tests=true \
  --tech-stack=typescript
```

### Development Workflow

```bash
# 1. Generate the project
copier copy {{ template_path }} ./my-project
cd ./my-project

# 2. Set up development environment{% if include_devbox %}
devbox shell{% else %}
# Install dependencies
{{ install_command }}{% endif %}

# 3. Run tests{% if include_tests %}
{{ test_command }}{% endif %}

# 4. Start development server{% if dev_server %}
{{ dev_server }}{% endif %}
```

### Customization Examples

#### Example 1: Minimal Project
```bash
copier copy {{ template_path }} ./minimal-project \
  --project-name=minimal-app \
  --include-tests=false \
  --include-docs=false
```

#### Example 2: Full-Featured Project
```bash
copier copy {{ template_path }} ./full-featured \
  --project-name=enterprise-app \
  --include-tests=true \
  --include-docs=true \
  --include-ci-cd=true \
  --tech-stack={{ tech_stack | first | default("typescript") }}
```

