## Contributing to This Template

### Template Development

When contributing to this template:

1. **Test changes**: Always test template generation with `copier copy`
2. **Update documentation**: Keep this `AGENTS.md.jinja` in sync with changes
3. **Version properly**: Update version in `copier.yaml` and documentation
4. **Follow conventions**: Use established patterns from other templates

### Template Structure

```
{{ template_path }}/
├── copier.yaml                   # Template configuration
├── files/                        # Template files
│   ├── {{ main_source }}/        # Main source code
│   ├── tests/                    # Test files
│   └── docs/                     # Documentation
├── README.md                     # Template documentation
└── AGENTS.md.jinja              # This file - agent documentation
```

### Testing Template Changes

```bash
# Test template generation
copier copy {{ template_path }} /tmp/test-{{ boilerplate_name }}

# Verify generated structure
cd /tmp/test-{{ boilerplate_name }}
tree -L 3

# Test build and functionality{% if include_devbox %}
devbox shell{% endif %}
{{ install_command }}
{{ test_command }}
```

